trans-unit.source: Choose a fixed fee for each order placed in %currency% with %module%.
trans-unit.target: Odaberite fiksnu naknadu za svaku narudžbu stavljenu u %currency% s %module%.

trans-unit.source: Choose a variable fee for each order placed in %currency% with %module%. It will be applied on the total paid with taxes.
trans-unit.target: Odaberite promjenjivu naknadu za svaku narudžbu postavljenu u %currency% s %module%. Biti će primijenjeno na ukupno plaćanje s porezom.

trans-unit.source: Choose a fixed fee for each order placed with a foreign currency with %module%.
trans-unit.target: Odaberite fiksnu naknadu za svaku narudžbu sa stranom valutom sa %module%.

trans-unit.source: Choose a variable fee for each order placed with a foreign currency with %module%. It will be applied on the total paid with taxes.
trans-unit.target: Odaberite promjenjivu naknadu za svaku narudžbu sa stranom valutom sa %module%. Biti će primijenjeno na ukupno plaćanje s porezom.
